reviewText: The storyline and plots are so very reminiscent of cartoons from the '80s, but the animation is ten times better. My kid loves this series, and although it doesn't have any rewatch value for me, my kid loves rewatching favorite episodes. From a child's point of view, this series is awesome!
Title: Hot Wheels Battle Force 5: Season 1, Vol. 1

reviewText: Good entertainment for our 6 YO grandson.  Not as much obvious violence as many of todays cartoons.  He enjoyed it thoroughly!

reviewerName: Karen B - mom of 5, including triplets!
reviewText: Great series of Hot Wheels Battle Force 5! Wish there were more than 4 episodes per DVD and wish they put more out on DVD. The toys you can buy are great too.
Title: Hot Wheels Battle Force 5: Season 1, Vol. 1

reviewText: We got this video just in time for a long road trip. It was a life (and sanity) saver! Hot Wheels Battle Force 5 has good lessons for young boys (or girls) to learn about teamwork, trust, self-reliance, and responsibility, all set in an action packed setting with diverse characters. The bad guys are mean, yet humorous at times, and the good guys always win.
Title: Hot Wheels Battle Force 5: Season 1, Vol. 1

reviewText: My son loved this series when it came on tv but was never able to watch them!! He was excited when he found them and he added them to his birthday list!! He was very happy to get them!!
